en_2078604_0	Four persons of the same family have been murdered in Dunuwila, Wennappuwa.
en_2078604_1	According to the office of the Police Media Spokesperson, two children are among the victims.
en_2078604_2	Police say that the hands and feet of the victims were bound and thereafter, their bodies had been dumped into a pit containing coconut husks.
en_2078604_3	Police also noted that one of the victims was a female doctor attached to the Lunuwila Hospital.
